data.description: Welcome to 957 33rd St. This quaint home is perfectly situated near shopping and US 131. Wonderfully maintained and updated, this is a lovely turnkey home located in the City of Wyoming. The back yard is much larger than you might expect and fully fenced. The oversized 1 stall garage is perfect for extra storage as well as keeping your car out of the winter weather. This home will not last long so schedule your private showing today!
